com.dinggoapplication.Fragments

Interface CustomerViewAll.OnDealFragmentInteractionListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EatDrinkActivity
    Enclosing class:
    CustomerViewAll

    public static interface CustomerViewAll.OnDealFragmentInteractionListener
    This interface must be implemented by activities that contain this fragment to allow an interaction in this fragment to be communicated to the activity and potentially other fragments contained in that activity.

    • Method Summary

      void onDealFragmentInteraction(java.lang.String id)
